Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.08,0:00:06.55,中文,,0,0,0,,饥渴 一位诗人曾说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hunger, a poet once said,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.28,0:00:09.99,中文,,0,0,0,,是我们所知最重要的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}is the most important thing we know,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:12.02,中文,,0,0,0,,也是我们所学的第一堂课\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the first lesson we learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:18.26,中文,,0,0,0,,但是饥渴容易被平复 容易被满足\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But hunger can be easily quieted down, easily satiated.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:22.97,中文,,0,0,0,,世上存在着另外一种力量 它算是一种特殊的饥渴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There is another force, a different type of hunger,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:27.37,中文,,0,0,0,,它难以遏制 无法磨灭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}an unquenchable thirst that cannot be extinguished.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.37,0:00:32.81,中文,,0,0,0,,它的存在造就了我们 我们才能称为“人”\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's very existence is what defines us, what makes us human.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:35.95,中文,,0,0,0,,这种力量就是 爱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That force is love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs50\pos(802,524)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}二{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}月{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)}8{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}号{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)} 初{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)}始{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.25,0:00:41.71,中文,,0,0,0,,各位旅客 我是本次航班的机长\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Folks, this is your captain up in the flight deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.86,0:00:45.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我们将准时降落终点纽约机场\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We are on our final descent into New York for an on-time arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:47.95,中文,,0,0,0,,感谢您乘坐里吉斯航空\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We want to thank you for flying Regis Air
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:49.46,中文,,0,0,0,,如果您需要转机口的信息\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and encourage that you ask us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:51.70,中文,,0,0,0,,欢迎各位乘客询问机组人员\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}any connecting gate information you may need.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:53.80,中文,,0,0,0,,机外此时为多云天气\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're looking at partly cloudy skies
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:56.86,中文,,0,0,0,,着陆时可能会受到轻微的气流影响\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and we may hit a little turbulence on our approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:00:58.20,中文,,0,0,0,,别再来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:02.97,中文,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:04.54,中文,,0,0,0,,罗斯 来后舱一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Rose get back here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:05.74,中文,,0,0,0,,我需要你的帮助\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.06,0:01:07.78,中文,,0,0,0,,我们准备降落呢 等会吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're landing, whatever it is can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.78,0:01:09.35,中文,,0,0,0,,现在来 马上来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now. Come now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.08,0:01:11.65,中文,,0,0,0,,好的好的 别激动\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:19.53,中文,,0,0,0,,先生 我们准备降落\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sir, we're landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:21.24,中文,,0,0,0,,请您关掉您的设备\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Would you power off your device?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.71,0:01:22.77,中文,,0,0,0,,你把它叫做设备么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You call this a device?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.82,0:01:23.93,中文,,0,0,0,,请您关掉它\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You have to turn it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:26.93,中文,,0,0,0,,就像警察把汽车称作车辆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's like when a cop calls a car a "Vehicle".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.11,0:01:31.15,中文,,0,0,0,,或是叫你先生的时候 其实是想说你是个混蛋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Or when he calls you sir when he means "Asshole".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:34.02,中文,,0,0,0,,我在纽约有场演出\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Having a little gig in New York coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:36.71,中文,,0,0,0,,你再给我三四瓶伏特加\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You give me three or four of those little baby vodkas
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.71,0:01:38.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我就给你前排的座位票\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll get you a front-row seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.73,0:01:40.21,中文,,0,0,0,,关掉它 座位调正\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Turn it off, put your seat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:42.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我们马上要降落了 先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're landing, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:46.75,中文,,0,0,0,,女士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:50.84,中文,,0,0,0,,请将座位调正\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Seat backs in the upright position.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:51.31,中文,,0,0,0,,终于到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:54.09,中文,,0,0,0,,机组人员注意 飞机准备着陆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Flight attendants, prepare for landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:56.97,中文,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:58.80,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要降落了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:01:59.59,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:02.72,中文,,0,0,0,,你真是个勇敢的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:05.77,中文,,0,0,0,,来 这给你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:06.56,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:07.69,中文,,0,0,0,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:10.61,中文,,0,0,0,,现在先把你的音乐关掉 我们要降落了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.35,中文,,0,0,0,,在此代表本次航班所有机组人员\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}On behalf of the cabin crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:15.51,中文,,0,0,0,,我想告知各位\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I want to take a moment to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.31,0:02:18.57,中文,,0,0,0,,彼得 你后舱都没有好好整理么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Peter, you haven't done anything back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:19.24,中文,,0,0,0,,这地方乱糟糟的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This place is a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:21.55,中文,,0,0,0,,-飞机上有东西 -什么意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- There's something in the plane. - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:23.31,中文,,0,0,0,,-有个生物在货仓里 -嘘嘘\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Something alive in the cargo hold! - Shh-shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:26.86,中文,,0,0,0,,和我们一起乘坐本次航班的黑铂金奖成员\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We'd like to extend a special thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:29.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我们表示由衷的谢意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to any Black Platinum Award mbers flying with us tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.91,0:02:32.40,中文,,0,0,0,,同时也欢迎所有乘客\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and encourage all our passengers...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:34.27,中文,,0,0,0,,你到底什么意思 是狗吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What the hell do you mean, like a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.27,0:02:36.27,中文,,0,0,0,,不是 是一种特别特别大的生物\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, it's something really, really big.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:37.64,中文,,0,0,0,,我听到他在动\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I heard it move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:39.86,中文,,0,0,0,,地板下有撞击声\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A thumping underneath the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:40.67,中文,,0,0,0,,我听到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I heard it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.67,0:02:43.07,中文,,0,0,0,,彼得 货物舱单上并未列有动物\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, Peter, there are no animals on the manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:44.61,中文,,0,0,0,,它想打开门闩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It tried to open the latch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:45.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我听到声音了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I heard a noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:47.00,中文,,0,0,0,,然后它就走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Then it moved away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.91,0:02:49.78,中文,,0,0,0,,但是你能感觉它在动\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But you can feel it moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:54.42,中文,,0,0,0,,请机组人员准备降落\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Flight crew prepare for arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:30.69,中文,,0,0,0,,你看到了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.66,中文,,0,0,0,,什么都没有 我觉得你在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nothing. I just think that you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:35.66,中文,,0,0,0,,哦天啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:37.36,中文,,0,0,0,,快去报告雷德芬机长\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Go tell Captain Redfern!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.13,中文,,0,0,0,,让他提醒地面人员\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Tell him to warn the landing crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:40.57,中文,,0,0,0,,启动紧急预案\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And get emergency services!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:42.50,中文,,0,0,0,,有东西在下面\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's someone down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:45.60,中文,,0,0,0,,它要出来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's gonna give!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:04:00.19,中文,,0,0,0,,D航空347次航班 可以使用F滑行道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Private Delta 3-4-7, you're clear for taxiway Foxtrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:04.09,中文,,0,0,0,,D航空347次航班 可以使用F滑行道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Private Delta 3-4-7, clear for taxiway Foxtrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:11.13,中文,,0,0,0,,里吉斯航空753次航班 这里是肯尼迪机场\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Regis Air 7-5-3, this is Kennedy ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:16.53,中文,,0,0,0,,里吉斯航空753次航班 这里是肯尼迪机场\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Regis Air 7-5-3, Kennedy ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:20.14,中文,,0,0,0,,里吉斯航空753次航班 这里是肯尼迪机场 请回话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Regis 7-5-3, Kennedy ground, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:24.34,中文,,0,0,0,,搞什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What the... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:27.71,中文,,0,0,0,,毕舍普\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Bishop...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.58,中文,,0,0,0,,柏林起飞的里吉斯航空\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}a Regis Air flight out of Berlin,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.02,中文,,0,0,0,,767宽体客机\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the 767 widebody,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:32.72,中文,,0,0,0,,停在了修护停机坪上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}stopped on the service apron.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:33.85,中文,,0,0,0,,它停在哪儿做什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What's it doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:34.92,中文,,0,0,0,,停机坪已经荒废了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Apron's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:35.71,中文,,0,0,0,,那里是不受保护的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's a blind spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:35.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:36.88,中文,,0,0,0,,那架飞机没有回应\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The plane just went dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:38.40,中文,,0,0,0,,完全没有任何消息\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}shut down, flat-out quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:40.30,中文,,0,0,0,,没有光 没有电波 什么都没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No lights, no radio, no nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:42.60,中文,,0,0,0,,里吉斯航空753次航班 这里是肯尼迪机场 请回话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Regis 7-5-3, Kennedy ground, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:46.00,中文,,0,0,0,,里吉斯航空753次航班 这里是肯尼迪机场 请回话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Regis 7-5-3- Kennedy ground, please respond, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:50.22,中文,,0,0,0,,关闭F滑行道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, shut down Foxtrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:52.42,中文,,0,0,0,,清空所有登机口 要求其他飞机改航\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Clear all the gates and advise reroute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:54.11,中文,,0,0,0,,机上有多少乘客\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How many aboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:55.87,中文,,0,0,0,,几乎满员\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Almost full flight, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:58.21,中文,,0,0,0,,乘客 机组人员 大约210人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Passengers, crew, about 210 souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:04:59.54,中文,,0,0,0,,上帝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Holy Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:01.85,中文,,0,0,0,,我们不应该先等警察来吗 先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Shouldn't we wait for first responders, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:15.13,中文,,0,0,0,,毕舍普\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Bishop?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:19.37,中文,,0,0,0,,毕舍普 等等\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Bishop, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:21.13,中文,,0,0,0,,引擎关了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Engines are shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:24.17,中文,,0,0,0,,没有光\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:32.48,中文,,0,0,0,,哇 真冷\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Whoa, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:36.73,中文,,0,0,0,,像死尸一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's like a dead animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:41.86,中文,,0,0,0,,这里很蹊跷\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's something really wrong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:45.72,中文,,0,0,0,,似乎这架飞机从未起飞过一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's like it never moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.29,中文,,0,0,0,,从这里看比\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This looks so much bigger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:49.13,中文,,0,0,0,,从屏幕上看大多了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}from the ground than on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:51.46,中文,,0,0,0,,就像一个带翅膀的建筑物一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I mean, they're like buildings with wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:56.57,中文,,0,0,0,,所有的遮光板都关着 看到了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All the window shades are shut, see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:05:58.67,中文,,0,0,0,,毕舍普\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Bishop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.44,中文,,0,0,0,,伙计们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:01.67,中文,,0,0,0,,毕舍普\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Bishop...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:04.11,中文,,0,0,0,,有一扇开着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Not all of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:17.62,中文,,0,0,0,,召集所有应急车辆到F滑行道上来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Scramble all emergency vehicles to taxiway Foxtrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:19.26,中文,,0,0,0,,包括特警队和国土安全部么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}SWAT, Homeland Security?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:21.63,中文,,0,0,0,,港务局 联邦调查局 运输安全局和疾控中心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Port Authority, FBI, TSA, CDC.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:24.03,中文,,0,0,0,,罗比 地面塔台上所有人都不许打电话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Robbie, no one on the tower calls home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:25.56,中文,,0,0,0,,全面封锁消息\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No one shares the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:28.51,中文,,0,0,0,,情况很糟 大事不妙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is bad, real bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:32.90,中文,,0,0,0,,这架飞机上应该是无人生还了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We've got ourselves a dead airplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs50\pos(802,524)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}皇后{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}区{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)}8{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}阿里{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)} 托斯{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)}33{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}街
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:13.70,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 哥们儿 你不能停在这 这有个防火栓\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, buddy, you can't park there. There's a fire hydrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:15.31,中文,,0,0,0,,医疗紧急情况\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's a medical emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:16.74,中文,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, is it really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:19.28,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我系不好我的领带那就是了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It will be if I can't get this tie on right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:20.40,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道怎么系吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know how to tie this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:21.88,中文,,0,0,0,,不知道 我带卡夹式的领带\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know, man, I wear a clip-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:24.13,中文,,0,0,0,,你自己搞定吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:24.88,中文,,0,0,0,,你在等人吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You waiting for somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:25.68,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:27.02,中文,,0,0,0,,那我需要你帮我个忙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Here's what I need you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:28.53,中文,,0,0,0,,交警要是来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The meter maid comes by,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:31.13,中文,,0,0,0,,你就跟她说这是疾控中心在处理公事 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you tell them it's official CDC business, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:32.90,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:35.82,中文,,0,0,0,,扎克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Zach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:37.84,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:45.24,中文,,0,0,0,,老兄\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:46.42,中文,,0,0,0,,你迟到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:48.00,中文,,0,0,0,,5分钟而已 我也没办法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Five minutes. It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:49.49,中文,,0,0,0,,是十分钟 爸爸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ten, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:50.79,中文,,0,0,0,,十分钟吗 好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ten? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:51.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你系错了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:53.22,中文,,0,0,0,,也许 也许是十分钟吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe... maybe ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:56.59,中文,,0,0,0,,我有种很好的预感\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I got a good feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:58.13,中文,,0,0,0,,祝我们好运\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Wish us luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.67,中文,,0,0,0,,好运\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:08.91,中文,,0,0,0,,迟到5分钟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:10.57,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道 我知道了 对不起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know, I know. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:11.68,中文,,0,0,0,,是十分钟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:14.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我给你发了五次短信\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I texted you five times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:15.45,中文,,0,0,0,,我没看到 我开车\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I wouldn't have gotten that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.01,中文,,0,0,0,,从不看短信\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}'cause I don't text when I drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:18.12,中文,,0,0,0,,这样不安全\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:19.35,中文,,0,0,0,,古德温泽博士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dr. Goodweather...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:20.45,中文,,0,0,0,,叫我伊弗就好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Eph, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:21.99,中文,,0,0,0,,你叫她凯莉 叫我儿子扎克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She gets Kelly, my son gets Zach,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:24.05,中文,,0,0,0,,所以叫我伊弗雷姆或者伊弗就行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}so Ephraim or Eph, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:27.48,中文,,0,0,0,,古德温泽博士 这是法院指定的六次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dr. Goodweather, this is the last of six
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:30.48,中文,,0,0,0,,抚养权咨询会议的最后一次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}court-appointed custody counselling sessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.77,中文,,0,0,0,,你四次都迟到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You've been late for four of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.80,中文,,0,0,0,,你是想说我是因为不想来所以才迟到的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Are you gonna say that I'm late because I don't want to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:36.73,中文,,0,0,0,,你也许有点想法 但是我真的有合理的原因\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You might be onto something but I have a really good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:38.57,中文,,0,0,0,,字母城幼儿园\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There was this outbreak of Hantavirus
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:40.20,中文,,0,0,0,,爆发了汉坦病毒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in this alphabet city pre-school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:42.51,中文,,0,0,0,,这在北部和东部是极其罕见的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Which is extremely rare this far north and east.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:44.41,中文,,0,0,0,,古德温泽博士 你每次来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dr. Goodweather, every time you come in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:45.94,中文,,0,0,0,,都要掌握话语权\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you take over the session.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:48.18,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我是控制狂 我知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Because I have control issues, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:49.91,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我必须为自己辩解\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But I have to defend myself here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:52.42,中文,,0,0,0,,因为也许这是我最后一次机会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Because this might be my last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:55.75,中文,,0,0,0,,关于这个问题我想了很久\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And I've thought long and hard about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:58.59,中文,,0,0,0,,看来你俩潜移默化的把我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And it seems like you two have created this narrative
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:09:00.39,中文,,0,0,0,,当成了坏人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}wherein I'm the bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:01.59,中文,,0,0,0,,但是为什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:04.56,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我不想离婚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Because I don't want out of my marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:08.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是想让事情回到原来的样子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}'Cause I want things back the way they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:11.46,中文,,0,0,0,,这件事不止是只涉及到你一个人 伊弗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But this isn't just about you, Eph,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:14.45,中文,,0,0,0,,也不是你想怎样就怎样的问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}what you want, not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:27.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我是流行病学家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm an epidemiologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:31.24,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我休假跑去钓鱼 会死人的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know, if I take time off, if I go fly-fishing, people die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:33.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你工作很重要 伊弗雷姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I get that you have an important job, Ephraim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.88,中文,,0,0,0,,你在你的工作领域十分出色\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And you're great at your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.61,中文,,0,0,0,,简直可以得满分\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You get straight 'A's at your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:40.11,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我在婚姻里表现不及格 对吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But I'm flunking our marriage, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:42.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你在写什么 别写了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What are you writing? Please stop writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:46.02,中文,,0,0,0,,我到底有多差\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How horrible am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:48.92,中文,,0,0,0,,你并不差\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're not horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:51.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你只是不着家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're just barely present.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:55.93,中文,,0,0,0,,我为了让你回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I've done everything you've asked me to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:58.80,中文,,0,0,0,,已经做了所有你要我做的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in order to get us back together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:10:00.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我戒了酒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I quit drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:02.74,中文,,0,0,0,,你想一个人呆着 所以我搬出去住\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You wanted time alone so I moved out,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:03.87,中文,,0,0,0,,尽管我本人并不想\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}against my own wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我对你言听计从\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I've jumped through every hoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:07.20,中文,,0,0,0,,你到底还想要什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Tell me what you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:09.15,中文,,0,0,0,,分居只是让我理清了一些事情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Our time apart has only clarified things for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:11.31,中文,,0,0,0,,让我认识了马特 让他走进我的生活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's allowed me to make room in my life for Matt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:12.84,中文,,0,0,0,,我们打算住在一起了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're going to be living together now and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:16.80,中文,,0,0,0,,马特 你说的是哪个西尔斯百货的销售员 住我家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Matt, the Sears guy you were talking about, at my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.57,中文,,0,0,0,,马特是业务经理\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Matt is an operational manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:19.22,中文,,0,0,0,,西尔斯百货的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}At Sears.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:20.42,中文,,0,0,0,,对 你知道的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, and you know what,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:22.32,中文,,0,0,0,,他在工作上的表现也很出色\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}he gets straight 'A's at his job, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:23.76,中文,,0,0,0,,但他也很着家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But at home, he's present.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:27.26,中文,,0,0,0,,不像你 他一直都在 陪着我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Unlike you, he's always here for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:31.46,中文,,0,0,0,,他是不是开着一辆绿色普锐斯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Does he drive a green Prius?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:41.64,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你要我辞职 我会辞职的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You want me to quit my job, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:42.74,中文,,0,0,0,,我会辞掉工作\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll quit my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:44.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我不想你为了我辞掉工作\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't want you to quit for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:45.71,中文,,0,0,0,,我不会为了你辞职\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I wouldn't be quitting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:47.68,中文,,0,0,0,,我是辞职是因为你 但是是为了扎克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'd be quitting because of you for Zach,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:49.35,中文,,0,0,0,,所以他没有开着一辆绿色普锐斯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}so he isn't driving around Queens
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:50.58,中文,,0,0,0,,在皇后区里转悠\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in a green goddamn Prius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:51.85,中文,,0,0,0,,古德温泽博士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dr. Goodweather.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:53.52,中文,,0,0,0,,太迟了 伊弗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's too late, Eph.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:55.26,中文,,0,0,0,,我爱你但是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I love you but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:57.99,中文,,0,0,0,,你还爱着我的话 又怎么会太迟呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How can you love me and it be too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:00.99,中文,,0,0,0,,你要一个疼爱扎克的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You want a guy who's crazy about Zach?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:02.03,中文,,0,0,0,,我是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:04.86,中文,,0,0,0,,一个疼爱你的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A guy who's crazy about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:06.30,中文,,0,0,0,,我是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:08.37,中文,,0,0,0,,正派得体 有正当工作\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Decent, employed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:10.67,中文,,0,0,0,,是 我都是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Check, check.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:25.09,中文,,0,0,0,,你还不懂这就是问题所在吗 伊弗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can't you see that this is the problem, Eph?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:29.09,中文,,0,0,0,,这就是你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:32.93,中文,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:49.21,中文,,0,0,0,,诺拉 情况有多糟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nora, how bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:50.54,中文,,0,0,0,,糟爆了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:52.81,中文,,0,0,0,,差不多有12个不同机构的官员\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have like 12 different agency officials
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.56,中文,,0,0,0,,抢着要负责这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}about to have a dick-measuring contest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:55.11,中文,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:57.59,中文,,0,0,0,,这是从柏林出发的国际航班\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's an international flight docking out of Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:11:58.95,中文,,0,0,0,,疾控中心最先收到通知\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}CDC gets the first call.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:00.69,中文,,0,0,0,,我20分钟内会到那里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can be there in 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:03.12,中文,,0,0,0,,这段时间内你能拖延一下检测工作吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can you keep the measuring contest going that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:05.16,中文,,0,0,0,,放心 我会让他们看看我的厉害\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Don't worry, I'll show them mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:08.00,中文,,0,0,0,,可能奏效吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It might just work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:12.00,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:15.84,中文,,0,0,0,,我猜抄表员不明白这是有多急\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I guess the meter reader didn't see it as much of an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:19.61,中文,,0,0,0,,马特 是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Matt, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.54,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 我是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.54,0:12:22.88,中文,,0,0,0,,有意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:25.55,中文,,0,0,0,,很遗憾我现在有急事 马特\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know, it's too bad I'm such a rush, Matt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.85,中文,,0,0,0,,但我可以肯定会在我家再见到你的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But I'm sure I'll see you again in my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:32.62,中文,,0,0,0,,开车小心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You drive safe now, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs50\pos(802,524)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}F{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}滑{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)}行{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:42.90,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 老大\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我的牛奶呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Got my milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:45.20,中文,,0,0,0,,在这\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Uh, yeah, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:47.40,中文,,0,0,0,,国土安全局急着想\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Homeland Security is just desperate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:49.37,中文,,0,0,0,,启动恐怖警报\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to push the button on a terror alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.64,中文,,0,0,0,,他们已经准备登机了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They're ready to get on that plane right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:54.21,中文,,0,0,0,,金 恐怖分子通常都会坠毁飞机\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Jim, terrorists usually crash planes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.81,中文,,0,0,0,,不会让飞机着陆并关掉引擎的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}not land them and shut them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:57.41,中文,,0,0,0,,报警的人怎么说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So what are the 911 calls saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:12:58.65,中文,,0,0,0,,没人报警\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There haven't been any.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:12:59.65,中文,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}None?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:00.68,中文,,0,0,0,,恩恩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Uh uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:01.78,中文,,0,0,0,,古德温泽博士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dr. Goodweather!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.42,中文,,0,0,0,,上周我们飞去芝加哥\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}When we flew to Chicago last week
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:05.25,中文,,0,0,0,,只不过在停机坪上坐了半个小时\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}we sat on the tarmac for half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:07.32,中文,,0,0,0,,群众就已经被吓坏了 开始发信息 打电话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}People were freaking out, texting, calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:09.92,中文,,0,0,0,,现在却有200个人静静的坐在上面\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There've been 200 people sitting there silently for...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:11.56,中文,,0,0,0,,超过一个小时\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}over an hour now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.59,中文,,0,0,0,,飞行员呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Pilots?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:13.79,中文,,0,0,0,,完全没有动静\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Absolutely no movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:15.33,中文,,0,0,0,,你做过红外线生命探测了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Have you done heat readings?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:16.90,中文,,0,0,0,,机体表层温度太冷了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Surface of the plane's too cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:18.40,中文,,0,0,0,,像个屏障似的把飞机封锁起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Blocks it all like a screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:19.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我们把音频探测仪伸到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We got Delsar mics attached
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:21.10,中文,,0,0,0,,表层进行探测\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to the surface of the plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:22.27,中文,,0,0,0,,几乎完全没有动静\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}picked up mostly silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:23.27,中文,,0,0,0,,几乎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mostly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:24.80,中文,,0,0,0,,有金属板\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, cooling pings
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.81,0:13:26.14,中文,,0,0,0,,受冷收缩的声音\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}from the sheet metal contracting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:27.81,中文,,0,0,0,,还有就是这个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, and there's this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:41.55,中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得这个是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:42.96,中文,,0,0,0,,某种东西发出的声音\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Rustling of some sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:45.26,中文,,0,0,0,,专家认为是引擎关闭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Our experts think it's the engine shutting down
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:46.36,中文,,0,0,0,,或者是液体沉降的声音\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}or liquids settling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:47.62,中文,,0,0,0,,从着陆到引擎关闭是多久的时间\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How long between landing and shutdown?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:48.24,中文,,0,0,0,,6分钟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Six minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:50.76,中文,,0,0,0,,时间太短 不足以让感染通过窗户蔓延\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's too short a window for a contagious event.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:53.50,中文,,0,0,0,,所以 我想疾控中心这次应该退居二线\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So I think CDC should take a back seat on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:54.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我同意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:55.94,中文,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:57.14,中文,,0,0,0,,当然了 我同意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Absolutely, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:58.97,中文,,0,0,0,,你多久会摸一次脸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How often do you touch your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:13:59.97,中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:01.21,中文,,0,0,0,,一天之内 多久摸一次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}In a day, how often?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:03.14,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道 大概一小时一次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know, once an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:04.95,中文,,0,0,0,,是每三分钟一次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Every three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:06.91,中文,,0,0,0,,你每五分钟就有一次手口碰触\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You have mouth/hand contact every five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:09.02,中文,,0,0,0,,每20分钟会跟其他人碰触一次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You touch somebody else every 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:10.55,中文,,0,0,0,,传染病就是这么传染的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's how contagion works.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:11.82,中文,,0,0,0,,你不喜欢恐怖分子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You don't like terrorists?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:13.25,中文,,0,0,0,,那试下跟病毒打交道吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Try negotiating with a virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:16.92,中文,,0,0,0,,一个病毒只有找到寄主才能存活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A virus exists only to find a carrier and reproduce.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:19.36,中文,,0,0,0,,它只会这么做 而且繁殖的很快\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's all it does and it does it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:20.96,中文,,0,0,0,,它可没有政治观\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It has no political views,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:23.66,中文,,0,0,0,,没有宗教信仰 没有文化障碍\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}it has no religious beliefs, it has no cultural hang-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:25.97,中文,,0,0,0,,它不鸟你们的军衔职位\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And it has no respect for a badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.97,0:14:28.60,中文,,0,0,0,,也没有时间和地理的概念\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It has no concept of time or geography.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:30.57,中文,,0,0,0,,它也许来自中世纪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It might as well be the Middle Ages,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:32.77,中文,,0,0,0,,随便搭个时间的便车\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}except for the convenience of hitching a ride
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:36.11,中文,,0,0,0,,就能在不同时代中穿梭 进行着一场又一场的杀戮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}on a metal tube flying from meal to meal to meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:39.00,中文,,0,0,0,,瘟疫就是着这样暴发的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's how a plague begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:43.42,中文,,0,0,0,,你还想第一个进入机舱吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So you still want to be the first one through the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs50\pos(758,526)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}曼{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}哈顿{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)} 哈姆莱{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}区{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)} 东{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)}118{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}街
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:11.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我们听说你买银器不要收据 老兄\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So we heard you buy silver without a receipt, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:12.68,中文,,0,0,0,,是这样吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:21.39,中文,,0,0,0,,好银器我永远都要 是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm always in need of good silver, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:23.53,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 那么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:27.40,中文,,0,0,0,,这玩意儿 我能卖个50刀吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can I get, uh, 50 for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:33.87,中文,,0,0,0,,这确实是一块很不错的表\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's a very nice timepiece, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:38.10,中文,,0,0,0,,表带已经断了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I see that the band links have snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:41.91,中文,,0,0,0,,你当时应该很急着把它摘下来吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You must have been in a hurry taking it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:44.46,中文,,0,0,0,,那它能卖50刀么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can I... can I get 50 for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:47.55,中文,,0,0,0,,我只能给你25刀\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can offer you maybe 25...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:50.25,中文,,0,0,0,,如果检查没有问题的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}if the test is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:58.02,中文,,0,0,0,,很不幸呀 只是表面镀了银的黄铜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Unfortunately, this is merely silver-plated brass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:16:01.13,中文,,0,0,0,,是东欧的伪劣仿制品\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A cheap Eastern European knock-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.43,0:16:03.46,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:05.67,中文,,0,0,0,,给我听好了 小子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Listen very carefully, son!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:07.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你的小伙伴那儿有枪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know your little friend has a gun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:09.54,中文,,0,0,0,,可能还上了膛 但我不在乎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and the hammer is cocked but I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.54,0:16:12.94,中文,,0,0,0,,我压住你这个穴位就能控制你整个人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can control your entire body weight from this pressure point
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:16.14,中文,,0,0,0,,而且我的这把刀直指你的桡动脉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and this knife is pointing straight at your radial artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:18.18,中文,,0,0,0,,一旦他掏出枪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}By the time he clears his coat pocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:21.05,中文,,0,0,0,,我就一刀下去 从头到尾\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}your artery will be punctured and sliced wide open
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:22.08,中文,,0,0,0,,切开你的动脉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}from top to bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:25.49,中文,,0,0,0,,你会倒在血泊里 我会躲到柜台底下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You fall down bleeding, I go under the counter
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.49,0:16:27.92,中文,,0,0,0,,你的小伙伴只能对着空气乱射\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and your friend starts shooting at an empty space.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:29.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我可以向你保证\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can guarantee you this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:32.29,中文,,0,0,0,,911接到报警电话之前 你就会失血而死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you will bleed out before the 911 operator answers the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:34.09,中文,,0,0,0,,这是选项一\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That is option one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:36.60,中文,,0,0,0,,还有选项二 你把钱放下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Option two is, you release the bills,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:38.67,中文,,0,0,0,,你的小伙伴把枪给我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}your friend gives me the gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:40.77,中文,,0,0,0,,他可以留下子弹 我不在乎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}he can keep the bullets, I don't care,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:42.37,中文,,0,0,0,,然后你们滚出我的店\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and you leave this store.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:46.46,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 孩子 你选吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now, son, you have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:06.83,中文,,0,0,0,,先生们 今晚还需要我为你们效劳些什么吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is there anything else I can do for you gentlemen this evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:22.31,中文,,0,0,0,,今晚发生在肯尼迪国际机场的事件\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We have more now on the developing story
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.31,中文,,0,0,0,,又有了新进展\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}out of JFK Airport tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:26.11,中文,,0,0,0,,您现在收看的是现场直播\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're looking at live video
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:29.38,中文,,0,0,0,,这架飞机是属于里吉斯航空公司的宽体客机\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of the airplane identified as a Regis Air widebody jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:31.15,中文,,0,0,0,,它从柏林起飞\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It originated in Berlin
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:34.65,中文,,0,0,0,,降落之后不久 就熄火了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and it shut down just moments after landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.71,0:17:37.28,中文,,0,0,0,,据我们所知 飞行员没有发出任何信号\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We are told there has been no communication from the pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:38.22,中文,,0,0,0,,与机组人员取得联络的一切努力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All attempts to contact the flight crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:39.46,中文,,0,0,0,,柏林\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Berlin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:00.17,中文,,0,0,0,,他又回来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:07.71,中文,,0,0,0,,我 呃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.18,0:19:11.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道我还有没有当初的力量\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know if I have the strength
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:12.95,中文,,0,0,0,,重新再来一次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to do it all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.46,0:19:23.96,中文,,0,0,0,,这一次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.96,0:19:25.57,中文,,0,0,0,,我决不能失败\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I cannot fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.37,0:19:36.08,中文,,0,0,0,,你饿了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Feeling hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:14.88,中文,,0,0,0,,享用吧 亲爱的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Enjoy, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\bord0\fs50\pos(802,524)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}肯尼迪{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}机场{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)}修{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}护{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)} 停{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)}机{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}坪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.89,0:20:42.13,中文,,0,0,0,,一会儿我们要面对的情况 可能会很糟糕\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm not looking forward to what we'll see out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:45.85,中文,,0,0,0,,你在听吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:49.48,中文,,0,0,0,,停机坪上有架死气沉沉的大客机 还不够刺激吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mysterious dead plane on the tarmac not exciting enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:53.05,中文,,0,0,0,,不好意思 刚从法院安排的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sorry, just another court-mandated,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:56.06,中文,,0,0,0,,离婚家庭心理治疗回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}happy family therapy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:59.23,中文,,0,0,0,,我注意到了 你还去理了发\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I noticed, you cut your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:00.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你还穿得整整齐齐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You cleaned up nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:02.91,中文,,0,0,0,,戴领带了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Did you break out a tie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:04.22,中文,,0,0,0,,在我外套口袋里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's in my jacket pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:06.55,中文,,0,0,0,,心理治疗有效果吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Did it help?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:08.46,中文,,0,0,0,,额 其实没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Uh, no, in fact, it didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.46,0:21:11.02,中文,,0,0,0,,她想带走扎克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She wants to take Zack away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:13.29,中文,,0,0,0,,而且还有个毛都没长全的家伙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And there's a... man-child
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:15.66,中文,,0,0,0,,住在我家里 和我儿子一起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}living in my house with my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:17.10,中文,,0,0,0,,小心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:21.94,中文,,0,0,0,,专心点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stay focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:27.84,中文,,0,0,0,,你和凯莉已经分居一年了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You and Kelly have been separated for a year,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:29.11,中文,,0,0,0,,这种情况很正常\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.11,0:21:30.31,中文,,0,0,0,,我们不也是这样么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It happened to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:31.61,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 不一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, that's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:32.71,中文,,0,0,0,,这怎么不一样了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How is it different?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.71,0:21:33.75,中文,,0,0,0,,就不一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It just is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:35.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得凯莉不会同意我们俩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't think Kelly would agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:37.28,中文,,0,0,0,,她不知道 我从没跟她说过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She doesn't know. I never told her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:38.35,中文,,0,0,0,,你没说过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.35,0:21:39.82,中文,,0,0,0,,没有 她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:41.62,中文,,0,0,0,,她提了离婚 所以我没告诉她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}she filed so I didn't tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:43.16,中文,,0,0,0,,她不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:48.09,中文,,0,0,0,,你真的一点都不了解女人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You really know nothing about women, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.04,0:22:04.78,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 老大\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:06.65,中文,,0,0,0,,准备好进去了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}ready to go through the looking glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.65,0:22:08.28,中文,,0,0,0,,准备好了 金\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ready, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.65,0:22:10.82,中文,,0,0,0,,我拿好你的牛奶了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I got your milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.99,0:22:14.25,中文,,0,0,0,,让它凉着 等我回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Keep it cold 'til I come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:50.56,中文,,0,0,0,,哦我的天呐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh my God...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:53.83,中文,,0,0,0,,金 你看到了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Jim, do you see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.46,0:22:57.24,中文,,0,0,0,,所有乘客 所有人都还在飞机上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's every passenger. Everyone on the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.40,0:22:57.82,中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.42,0:22:59.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我们正在看\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.62,0:23:01.30,中文,,0,0,0,,他们都死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They're all dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:04.20,中文,,0,0,0,,到底是什么 艾弗 是什么要了他们的命\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What is it, Eph? What killed them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.21,0:23:05.84,中文,,0,0,0,,没有挣扎的痕迹\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No signs of struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.84,0:23:09.41,中文,,0,0,0,,皮肤上没有水疱 没有化学药剂的痕迹\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No signs of blistering or chemical agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.41,0:23:10.84,中文,,0,0,0,,没有淤青\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No bruising.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.62,0:23:17.68,中文,,0,0,0,,也没有可见的变色\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Not seeing discoloration...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.84,0:23:19.95,中文,,0,0,0,,没有痕迹\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}no markings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.60,0:23:22.73,中文,,0,0,0,,妈蛋 到底是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Shit, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:26.73,中文,,0,0,0,,瞬间致命 毫无痛楚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Something sudden, painless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.66,0:23:35.00,中文,,0,0,0,,所有的遮光板都关着 除了这一扇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All the window shades are closed except for this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:39.37,中文,,0,0,0,,是气体泄漏吗 是化学毒气吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is it a gas leak? Is it chemical?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.37,0:23:42.08,中文,,0,0,0,,探测器检测到了高浓度的氨\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The Hazmat Cat's picking up high levels of ammonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.08,0:23:43.54,中文,,0,0,0,,但还不足以致命\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nothing deadly, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.54,0:23:46.08,中文,,0,0,0,,飞机的系统不可能出现氨\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There shouldn't be any ammonia in the plane systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.08,0:23:47.61,中文,,0,0,0,,金 查一下货仓的运单\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Jim, check the cargo manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.62,0:23:48.75,中文,,0,0,0,,明白\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.75,0:23:50.32,中文,,0,0,0,,我要一份货仓运单\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I need a cargo manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.32,0:23:51.52,中文,,0,0,0,,盖革计数器有反应吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What about the Geiger?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.52,0:23:53.22,中文,,0,0,0,,没有反应  金\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's negative, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.67,0:24:17.28,中文,,0,0,0,,没有可见的创伤\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No visible signs of trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.15,0:24:29.97,中文,,0,0,0,,没有肿胀\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No bloating.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.23,0:24:36.96,中文,,0,0,0,,舌头和软腭颜色暗淡 几乎发白\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Tongue and soft palate appear pale, almost white.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.50,0:24:45.00,中文,,0,0,0,,眼球很清澈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Eyes are clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.51,0:24:49.38,中文,,0,0,0,,皮肤干燥 没有弹性\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The skin is dry, it's inelastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.38,0:24:51.88,中文,,0,0,0,,没有起泡 没有鼻血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's no frothing or nosebleeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.15,0:24:55.01,中文,,0,0,0,,没有挣扎的痕迹\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's no signs of struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.12,0:24:57.62,中文,,0,0,0,,非常平静\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Almost peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.22,0:25:03.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我们试试紫外照射\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let's try the UV lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.00,0:25:17.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我的天呐 什么东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My God, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.11,0:25:23.74,中文,,0,0,0,,你们看到了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Are you getting this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.74,0:25:26.35,中文,,0,0,0,,到处都是这些痕迹\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}These patterns are everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.35,0:25:28.25,中文,,0,0,0,,整个机舱都是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All over the cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.25,0:25:30.72,中文,,0,0,0,,只有紫外照射下才看得见\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They're only visible under UV light.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.72,0:25:33.65,中文,,0,0,0,,这些是生物体的痕迹\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The pattern is biological.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.16,0:25:39.03,中文,,0,0,0,,可能是氨的来源\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Probably where the ammonia is coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.19,0:25:41.86,中文,,0,0,0,,我来采样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm taking samples.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.84,0:25:44.51,中文,,0,0,0,,你来采前舱的 我采后舱的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You take the front galley, I'll take the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.26,0:26:38.20,中文,,0,0,0,,吉宝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Jimbo...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.85,0:26:40.39,中文,,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.26,0:26:43.51,中文,,0,0,0,,请别叫我吉宝好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, "Jimbo, please"?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.89,0:26:48.39,中文,,0,0,0,,额 这是货仓区\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Um, that's the cargo compartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.40,0:26:49.80,中文,,0,0,0,,把它清空\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Have it emptied.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.80,0:26:51.76,中文,,0,0,0,,把每一件行李都带回去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Take each piece of luggage
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.77,0:26:54.47,中文,,0,0,0,,进行生物检测和氨谱检测\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and check it for biological agents and ammonia spectrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.47,0:26:55.73,中文,,0,0,0,,了解\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.27,0:27:28.23,中文,,0,0,0,,金\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Jim...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.24,0:27:30.64,中文,,0,0,0,,驾驶舱门开了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the cockpit door just opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.41,0:27:33.35,中文,,0,0,0,,它应该是关着的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It should be locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.97,0:27:35.42,中文,,0,0,0,,诺拉 那扇门不应该是开着的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nora, that door's not supposed to be open.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.40,0:27:39.45,中文,,0,0,0,,我就进去看一眼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just going to take a quick look.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.45,0:27:41.93,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 我要你立刻离开驾驶舱 听到了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Alright, I want you back out of there right now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.02,0:27:44.62,中文,,0,0,0,,那扇门应该是锁上的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That door is supposed to be locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.62,0:27:46.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你不能一个人进去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You shouldn't be in there alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.62,0:27:50.16,中文,,0,0,0,,诺拉 你听到了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nora, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.16,0:27:51.42,中文,,0,0,0,,艾弗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Eph!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.42,0:27:52.99,中文,,0,0,0,,驾驶舱的门开着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The door to the cockpit is open.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.99,0:27:54.39,中文,,0,0,0,,诺拉在里面\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nora is inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.53,0:28:01.77,中文,,0,0,0,,诺拉 艾弗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nora? Eph?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.54,0:28:05.67,中文,,0,0,0,,拜托啊同志们 回答我啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on, guys, somebody talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.88,0:28:13.08,中文,,0,0,0,,诺拉 我过来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nora, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.72,0:28:16.88,中文,,0,0,0,,救救我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.88,0:28:19.45,中文,,0,0,0,,女士 别拿灯照我脸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Lady, get the light outta my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.32,0:28:22.82,中文,,0,0,0,,我要让特种部队进来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm sending in SWAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.82,0:28:24.32,中文,,0,0,0,,别 金 让医疗队进来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, Jim, send paramedics!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.32,0:28:26.13,中文,,0,0,0,,发现幸存者了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We've got survivors!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.01,0:28:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\bord0\fs50\pos(412,528)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}石心{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}集团\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)}曼哈顿{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}57街{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)} 西{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)}156{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}号
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.80,0:29:00.17,中文,,0,0,0,,帕尔默先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mr. Palmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.17,0:29:02.61,中文,,0,0,0,,嘘 他正在做血液透析\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Shh! It's his dialysis session.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.61,0:29:04.47,中文,,0,0,0,,他睡着了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.47,0:29:06.58,中文,,0,0,0,,那就把他叫醒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, then wake him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.58,0:29:07.98,中文,,0,0,0,,等他透析结束吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}When he's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.98,0:29:09.21,中文,,0,0,0,,现在就叫醒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.21,0:29:10.71,中文,,0,0,0,,时间到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}In time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.15,0:29:14.02,中文,,0,0,0,,透析完毕\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dialysis complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.02,0:29:17.55,中文,,0,0,0,,你为石心集团效力多久了 菲茨威廉先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How long have you worked for Stoneheart, Mr. Fitzwilliam?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.55,0:29:19.46,中文,,0,0,0,,毕生效力 先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All my life, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.46,0:29:22.06,中文,,0,0,0,,我父亲去世之后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mr. Palmer aided me and my brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.06,0:29:23.96,中文,,0,0,0,,是帕尔默先生帮助了我和我弟弟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}after my father passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.96,0:29:27.76,中文,,0,0,0,,感恩 真是一种有效的契约\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Gratitude, what an effective leash.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.63,0:29:31.83,中文,,0,0,0,,艾霍斯特先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Herr Eichhorst...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.07,0:29:41.71,中文,,0,0,0,,帕尔默先生 艾霍斯特先生来探望您了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mr. Palmer, Herr Eichhorst is here to pay his respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.18,0:29:47.02,中文,,0,0,0,,如果您有需要的话 我就在门外\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll be outside if you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.59,0:29:53.62,中文,,0,0,0,,你可能注意到了这儿有点冷 艾霍斯特\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You may notice how chilly it has gotten in here, Eichhorst.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.62,0:29:56.53,中文,,0,0,0,,比大楼里的其他地方 都要低20度\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Twenty full degrees cooler than the rest of the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.53,0:29:58.69,中文,,0,0,0,,不过对你来说不算冷 我相信\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But not too cold for you, I trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.70,0:30:04.03,中文,,0,0,0,,当然 你根本不会觉得冷 是吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Of course, it can't be too cold for you, can it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.03,0:30:06.57,中文,,0,0,0,,货物已经安全抵达\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The cargo has arrived safely
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.57,0:30:09.94,中文,,0,0,0,,四个幸存者也被找到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and all four survivors have been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.34,0:30:12.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我这辈子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Throughout my life
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.91,0:30:16.31,中文,,0,0,0,,已经学会了越界行事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I've learned what it feels to cross a line,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.31,0:30:18.05,中文,,0,0,0,,是什么感觉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.05,0:30:21.25,中文,,0,0,0,,那些不可回头之事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Things that cannot be undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.29,0:30:25.55,中文,,0,0,0,,那条界\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That line...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.89,0:30:29.99,中文,,0,0,0,,已经越过了 是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}it has been crossed now, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.59,0:30:33.26,中文,,0,0,0,,我一直不能习惯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Your breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.26,0:30:35.80,中文,,0,0,0,,没有呼吸的你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll never get used to...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.47,0:30:40.80,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 即使是我自己都会怀念呼吸的感觉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yes, even I miss breathing sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.88,0:30:47.28,中文,,0,0,0,,他到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.35,0:30:54.45,中文,,0,0,0,,交给我吧 很快的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Leave it to me, it won't be long.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.16,0:31:03.09,中文,,0,0,0,,艾弗雷特\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Everett.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.19,0:31:05.09,中文,,0,0,0,,艾弗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Eph.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.40,0:31:08.13,中文,,0,0,0,,情况有多糟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.40,0:31:14.14,中文,,0,0,0,,国家运输安全委员会接管了布朗克斯区的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The NTSB has taken over a refrigerated chemical warehouse
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.14,0:31:15.77,中文,,0,0,0,,一间化学药剂冷藏库\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in the Bronx.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.77,0:31:18.71,中文,,0,0,0,,并把它改造成了巨大的停尸房\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They've turned it into a fully contained mass casualty morgue.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.71,0:31:20.21,中文,,0,0,0,,没有必要捂这口鼻 艾弗雷特\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's not necessary, Everett.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.21,0:31:21.64,中文,,0,0,0,,这些尸体袋经过了三层密封\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}These bags are triple-sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.64,0:31:23.71,中文,,0,0,0,,我要把12具尸体移交给医学继续教育机构\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm handing a dozen bodies over to the CME
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.71,0:31:25.55,中文,,0,0,0,,机舱三个部位各取四具\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}four from each section of the plane
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.55,0:31:26.62,中文,,0,0,0,,请他们做尸检\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}for autopsies.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.62,0:31:28.08,中文,,0,0,0,,四个幸存者怎么样了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And the four survivors?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.08,0:31:30.55,中文,,0,0,0,,我在本地医院安排了隔离病房\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I've secured the isolation rooms at a local hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.55,0:31:32.42,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要立刻把他们送过去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We need to move them there right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.42,0:31:34.29,中文,,0,0,0,,他们当然会好好配合的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Of course. I'm sure they'll comply.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.29,0:31:35.86,中文,,0,0,0,,配合 我不用要求他们配合\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Comply? I'm not asking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.86,0:31:38.66,中文,,0,0,0,,根据健康权力法案 他们必须隔离\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Invoking the Health Powers Act, those four survivors stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.66,0:31:40.33,中文,,0,0,0,,隔离\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Quarantine?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.33,0:31:43.67,中文,,0,0,0,,这在疾控中心的权力范围之内的 艾弗雷特 你是知道的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's within the powers of the CDC, Everett, you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.88,0:31:46.11,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 如果你要进行隔离\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look, if you quarantine
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.15,0:31:48.66,中文,,0,0,0,,我需要你和他们家属会面\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I need you to meet with the next of kin.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.68,0:31:49.71,中文,,0,0,0,,让他们放心 告诉他们疾控中心正在处理\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Reassure them the CDC's on the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.77,0:31:50.11,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.51,0:31:52.21,中文,,0,0,0,,我们正在想办法弄清\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're trying to figure out what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.21,0:31:52.88,中文,,0,0,0,,事情的来龙去脉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}what caused this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.08,0:31:55.55,中文,,0,0,0,,-难道这不是最重要的事情吗 -是的当然\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Isn't that what's most important? - Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.55,0:31:58.31,中文,,0,0,0,,但防止大规模恐慌 也很重要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But it's also important we don't have full-tilt panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.32,0:32:00.85,中文,,0,0,0,,这些人需要专家向他们解释\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}These people need to hear from someone in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.85,0:32:02.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我们什么都还没搞清楚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We don't know anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.25,0:32:04.73,中文,,0,0,0,,你们俩好好商量 我没空管这种破事儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You two figure this out. I don't have time for this shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.91,0:32:05.96,中文,,0,0,0,,-金 -好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Jim? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.96,0:32:07.71,中文,,0,0,0,,他会见家属的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}When he talks to the families,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.91,0:32:09.66,中文,,0,0,0,,我不想媒体在场 艾弗雷特\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I want no press, Everett.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.33,0:32:11.97,中文,,0,0,0,,不会有媒体 我保证\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No press, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.18,0:32:27.94,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 你说只有四个人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, you're telling me only four people
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.95,0:32:29.85,中文,,0,0,0,,在空难中生还\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}survived this plane crash?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.85,0:32:30.91,中文,,0,0,0,,卢斯小姐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ms. Luss...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.91,0:32:32.28,中文,,0,0,0,,是卢斯夫人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It Mrs. Luss.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.28,0:32:33.98,中文,,0,0,0,,卢斯夫人 不是空难\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mrs. Luss, there was no crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.98,0:32:35.52,中文,,0,0,0,,一种不明化学药物\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}An unidentified agent
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.52,0:32:37.39,中文,,0,0,0,,杀死了其他所有乘客\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}killed all of the remaining passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.39,0:32:40.02,中文,,0,0,0,,你能提供的任何信息 都会非常有帮助\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Any information you can give us would be of great help.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.02,0:32:41.39,中文,,0,0,0,,对谁非常有帮助\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Of great help to who?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.39,0:32:42.86,中文,,0,0,0,,对我们 夫人 疾控中心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}To us, ma'am, the CDC.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.86,0:32:44.76,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 我可不是普通的乘客\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, well, I'm no ordinary passenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.76,0:32:46.13,中文,,0,0,0,,我是琼·卢斯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm Joan Luss.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.13,0:32:50.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我是马特罗夫·卢斯·海恩公司的合伙律师\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm an attorney... of Matloff, Luss and Hayum.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.83,0:32:51.90,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你搜集到的一切信息\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So all that information that you're collecting
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.90,0:32:53.70,中文,,0,0,0,,都要给我一份\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you're going to need to get to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.70,0:32:54.90,中文,,0,0,0,,就个人来说...\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Personally...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.37,0:32:57.47,中文,,0,0,0,,你在做什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.47,0:32:59.64,中文,,0,0,0,,别把我封进来 我在和你说话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Don't seal me in, I'm talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.64,0:33:02.15,中文,,0,0,0,,不好意思 小女士 你不许走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Excuse me, little miss. Don't you walk away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.15,0:33:03.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我可是琼·卢斯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I am Joan Luss.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.62,0:33:07.82,中文,,0,0,0,,雷德芬机长 这是我的同事 马丁内斯博士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Captain Redfern, this is my colleague, Dr. Martinez.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.02,0:33:10.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我的飞机怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What happened on my plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.55,0:33:11.93,中文,,0,0,0,,我们正是想来问你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's what we came to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.26,0:33:15.39,中文,,0,0,0,,我要你尽力回忆一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now, I want you to try to recall, as best you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.39,0:33:18.23,中文,,0,0,0,,刚割的草 大蒜 青苹果\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}fresh cut grass, garlic, green apple...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.23,0:33:20.40,中文,,0,0,0,,你记不记得昏迷之前\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}do you remember smelling any of these odors
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.40,0:33:22.03,中文,,0,0,0,,闻到过这些味道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}before you passed out?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.03,0:33:24.07,中文,,0,0,0,,啥 草 苹果\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What? Grass? Apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.07,0:33:26.80,中文,,0,0,0,,气味特征 这是大脑记住某种气味的方式\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mnemonic odors, the way our brain reads chemicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.80,0:33:30.21,中文,,0,0,0,,磷化氢气体 无色 有大蒜气味\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Phosphine gas, colorless, smells like garlic.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.21,0:33:33.11,中文,,0,0,0,,剧毒的碳酰氯气体 刚割下的草的气味\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Or phosgene very toxic, smells like freshly cut grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.21,0:33:34.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我记得我把飞机降落\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I remember landing the plane
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.88,0:33:36.45,中文,,0,0,0,,转到滑行跑道上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and turning onto the taxiway.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.45,0:33:38.25,中文,,0,0,0,,然后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.25,0:33:40.85,中文,,0,0,0,,我就什么都不记得了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't remember anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.85,0:33:43.12,中文,,0,0,0,,艾弗 你能过来一下吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Eph, can I get you for a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.25,0:33:45.39,中文,,0,0,0,,哦谢天谢地 你来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, thank God, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.39,0:33:46.49,中文,,0,0,0,,我刚跟他说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I was just telling him
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.49,0:33:47.86,中文,,0,0,0,,我脑子里面\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have this noise in my head
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.86,0:33:49.09,中文,,0,0,0,,有嗡嗡嗡的声音\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}like a hum.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.09,0:33:51.33,中文,,0,0,0,,你能再请人过来检查一下我耳朵吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Could you have someone look at my ears again?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.33,0:33:53.42,中文,,0,0,0,,我们会给你做全面检查\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We'll have somebody perform a full battery of tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.46,0:33:56.70,中文,,0,0,0,,不过现在 请你待在棚子里别出来 巴伯尔先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But for now you need to stay inside this tent, Mr. Barbour.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.70,0:33:57.97,中文,,0,0,0,,你不明白\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.97,0:34:00.04,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我不打电话回家 我老婆会发疯的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My wife is gonna panic if I don't call soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.04,0:34:01.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我要打个电话回家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I need to call home.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.20,0:34:02.71,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 就是你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.01,0:34:06.51,中文,,0,0,0,,你是管事儿的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're the guy I gotta talk to around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.51,0:34:08.14,中文,,0,0,0,,额 我想是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Uh, yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.14,0:34:09.91,中文,,0,0,0,,给我点止痛药怎么样 医生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How about some Demerol, Doc, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.91,0:34:12.88,中文,,0,0,0,,还有 餐车什么时候过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And what time's that refreshment cart swing by, uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.88,0:34:15.72,中文,,0,0,0,,玻利瓦尔先生 在飞机降落前\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mr. Bolivar, what is the last thing you can remember
