Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.88,0:43:09.41,中文,,0,0,0,,这次不一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.15,0:43:14.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我得确定\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I need to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.95,0:43:17.72,中文,,0,0,0,,你每一步都按照我的指示去做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you follow my instructions precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.72,0:43:19.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我这儿有你哥哥的犯罪记录\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Your brother's criminal record
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.92,0:43:23.32,中文,,0,0,0,,还有你妈妈的移民身份证明\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and your mother's immigration status.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.23,0:43:26.93,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你是在威胁我的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If this is a threat
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.93,0:43:29.56,中文,,0,0,0,,那你就大错特错了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you just made a mistake, puto.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.56,0:43:33.67,中文,,0,0,0,,我不是在威胁你 我是在奖励你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It is not a threat. It is more a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.07,0:43:37.10,中文,,0,0,0,,剩下的酬劳在杂物箱里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The rest of your fee is in the glove box.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.10,0:43:39.21,中文,,0,0,0,,那辆车的导航系统上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Destination is pre-programmed
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.21,0:43:41.41,中文,,0,0,0,,已经输好了目的地\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}on the GPS in the vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.28,0:43:46.78,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我开失窃车被逮住了 我就玩完了 老兄\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I get picked up driving a stolen van, that's it, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.78,0:43:49.38,中文,,0,0,0,,我又会被扔回去蹲牢房的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They gonna send me back to the bull pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.78,0:43:51.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我不能再坐牢了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.02,0:43:54.39,中文,,0,0,0,,这活儿干不了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can't do it, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.16,0:44:00.09,中文,,0,0,0,,不是失窃车\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It is not stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.09,0:44:02.66,中文,,0,0,0,,你一路会畅通无阻\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You will be let through
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.66,0:44:04.36,中文,,0,0,0,,而且事后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and at the end of it
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.37,0:44:08.10,中文,,0,0,0,,你妈妈的移民问题就解决了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}your mother's immigration status will be fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.10,0:44:11.91,中文,,0,0,0,,你哥哥的犯罪记录也一笔勾销\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Your brother's criminal record erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.18,0:44:18.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我干 干完我就金盆洗手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I do this for you, that's it, I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.48,0:44:20.08,中文,,0,0,0,,删了我的电话号码和地址\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Lose my number and my address.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.08,0:44:22.58,中文,,0,0,0,,我现在得为妈妈做点事儿了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm trying to do the right thing by my mother now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.58,0:44:24.45,中文,,0,0,0,,如果她发生了什么事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}'Cause if anything happens to her
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.45,0:44:27.46,中文,,0,0,0,,哪怕一点点小事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I mean, anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.07,0:44:31.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我就废了你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll kill your waxy ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.46,0:44:32.83,中文,,0,0,0,,三个规矩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Three rules...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.14,0:44:36.51,中文,,0,0,0,,不许偷看货物\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you will not examine the cargo.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.51,0:44:38.85,中文,,0,0,0,,中途不许停车\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You will not make any stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.85,0:44:41.28,中文,,0,0,0,,最后是你必须在黎明前\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And you will cross the bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.28,0:44:44.72,中文,,0,0,0,,开过桥回到曼哈顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}back into Manhattan before daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.72,0:44:46.55,中文,,0,0,0,,懂了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.06,0:44:51.02,中文,,0,0,0,,你清楚复述一遍 三条规定\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}In English then, the three rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.13,0:44:55.11,中文,,0,0,0,,去你的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Screw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.82,0:44:57.84,中文,,0,0,0,,吃屎吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Suck my dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.10,0:45:01.87,中文,,0,0,0,,任务妥妥完成\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.19,0:45:20.78,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\bord0\fs50\pos(742,536)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}肯尼迪{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}机场{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)} 4{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}号{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)}航{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)}站{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}楼
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.20,0:45:38.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我女儿在那班飞机上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My daughter was on that flight!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.51,0:45:43.71,中文,,0,0,0,,玻利瓦尔 玻利瓦尔 玻利瓦尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Bolivar! Bolivar! Bolivar!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.58,0:45:53.35,中文,,0,0,0,,先生 机场的这部分区域已经封锁了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sir, this area of the airport is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.35,0:45:55.62,中文,,0,0,0,,你得和其他人一样在这里等着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You have to wait back there with everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.62,0:45:57.22,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 安静点 行不行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, settle down, will ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.09,0:46:01.09,中文,,0,0,0,,玻利瓦尔 玻利瓦尔 玻利瓦尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Bolivar! Bolivar! Bolivar!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.72,0:46:29.22,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 先生 先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, sir! Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.13,0:46:31.68,中文,,0,0,0,,先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.55,0:46:35.26,中文,,0,0,0,,没事 麻烦去找个轮椅\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's alright, sorry, just go get a wheelchair.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.26,0:46:36.66,中文,,0,0,0,,他是个病人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He's a medical.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.66,0:46:37.83,中文,,0,0,0,,你还好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.83,0:46:39.30,中文,,0,0,0,,先生 我看看你都有什么药\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sir, what do you have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.30,0:46:40.77,中文,,0,0,0,,你有 法华林\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You have... Coumadin.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.77,0:46:42.44,中文,,0,0,0,,你心脏有问题吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You got a heart condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.44,0:46:44.17,中文,,0,0,0,,还好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.51,0:46:47.84,中文,,0,0,0,,你是这儿的头吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Are you in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.84,0:46:49.18,中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.18,0:46:52.55,中文,,0,0,0,,我得找个人说说那架飞机的事儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I need to talk to someone about that plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.68,0:46:59.09,中文,,0,0,0,,头等舱的有几个人我认识\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I recognize some of these names in First Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.69,0:47:01.89,中文,,0,0,0,,不过没什么用\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That never helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.29,0:47:07.66,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 伊弗 你就介绍一下你自己\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look, Eph, just introduce yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.66,0:47:09.76,中文,,0,0,0,,然后说我们正在着手调查\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and tell them we're on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.76,0:47:11.37,中文,,0,0,0,,你能应付的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You'll do great.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.57,0:47:13.60,中文,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.37,0:47:30.80,中文,,0,0,0,,你刚才说没有媒体的时候 我差点就信了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}When you said no press, I almost believed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.36,0:47:42.23,中文,,0,0,0,,我是伊弗雷姆 古德温泽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm Ephraim Goodweather.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.23,0:47:43.86,中文,,0,0,0,,是纽约疾病控制中心的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm the Chief Medical Officer
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.87,0:47:46.70,中文,,0,0,0,,首席医疗官\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}for the Centers for Disease Control here in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.70,0:47:48.67,中文,,0,0,0,,我受命来此做个自我介绍\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have been asked to introduce myself
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.67,0:47:50.67,中文,,0,0,0,,并且初步解释一下当前的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and to give you a preliminary update on...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.67,0:47:52.21,中文,,0,0,0,,有多少幸存者\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How many survivors?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.01,0:47:56.31,中文,,0,0,0,,别这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.41,0:48:00.11,中文,,0,0,0,,别这样 别这样 别这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Please, please, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.62,0:48:09.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道我在这是应该说点安慰你们的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I think I'm supposed to stand here and somehow reassure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.46,0:48:12.83,中文,,0,0,0,,可我说不出\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.33,0:48:18.33,中文,,0,0,0,,753号航班上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Two hundred and six passengers
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.33,0:48:21.00,中文,,0,0,0,,206名乘客遇难\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}on  Air flight 753 are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.00,0:48:22.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我们不知道原因\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And we don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.60,0:48:26.81,中文,,0,0,0,,有四名活了下来 我们也不知道为什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Four passengers survived, and we don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.81,0:48:28.38,中文,,0,0,0,,但作为第一个登上该飞机的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What I can tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.38,0:48:30.34,中文,,0,0,0,,我只能告诉你们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}having been the first to board the plane
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.35,0:48:32.85,中文,,0,0,0,,他们都走得很平静\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}is that they all appeared to have died peacefully
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.85,0:48:34.38,中文,,0,0,0,,没有承受多大痛苦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}without distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.38,0:48:37.12,中文,,0,0,0,,这也是目前我能给大家的唯一的安慰了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's the only comfort I can give you at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.85,0:48:40.32,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你们想知道为什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You want answers
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.32,0:48:42.92,中文,,0,0,0,,想知道那班飞机上到底发生了什么 我也想知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}real answers to what happened on that plane and so do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.92,0:48:45.23,中文,,0,0,0,,在我们都有一个满意的答案前我绝不罢休\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And I won't quite until we're all satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.79,0:48:48.43,中文,,0,0,0,,我才不管这些大话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't care about your promises!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.43,0:48:50.26,中文,,0,0,0,,我只想要回我的女儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I want my daughter back!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.27,0:48:53.27,中文,,0,0,0,,你们只会说啊说 你们只会说大话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All you do is talk and talk! That's all you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.77,0:48:58.41,中文,,0,0,0,,这是我的女儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.41,0:49:00.21,中文,,0,0,0,,我的女儿 艾玛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My daughter, Emma!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.21,0:49:03.38,中文,,0,0,0,,我要见她 活要见人 死要见尸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And I want to see her again, dead, alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.38,0:49:05.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我是她的父亲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm her father!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.12,0:49:08.78,中文,,0,0,0,,你难道自己没有孩子吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Don't you have children of your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.78,0:49:11.22,中文,,0,0,0,,你良心被狗吃了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Don't you have a heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.69,0:49:21.60,中文,,0,0,0,,给我48小时 我会查出来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Forty-eight hours, I'll get your answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.60,0:49:23.00,中文,,0,0,0,,这是我所能做的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's the best I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.00,0:49:24.06,中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.56,0:49:32.11,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\bord0\fs50\pos(406,530)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}\h\h首席{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}法医{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)}办公室\N{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}曼哈顿{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)} 东{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)}30{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}街
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.30,0:49:30.67,中文,,0,0,0,,天 古德温泽 你这时候找我干嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Jesus! Goodweather, what are you doing to me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.67,0:49:32.21,中文,,0,0,0,,跟我说说你发现了些什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just tell me what you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.21,0:49:33.71,中文,,0,0,0,,我才开始呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm just getting into it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.71,0:49:35.74,中文,,0,0,0,,我还没有解剖完呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I haven't finished cutting all of them yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.74,0:49:37.48,中文,,0,0,0,,那就跟我说说你已经发现的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just give me anything you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.48,0:49:40.08,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 首先是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, top of the charts...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.08,0:49:41.38,中文,,0,0,0,,看这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.35,0:49:46.35,中文,,0,0,0,,你能看到这个吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can you see this here?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.69,0:49:49.29,中文,,0,0,0,,能 那是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.69,0:49:51.93,中文,,0,0,0,,是个切口\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's an incision.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.93,0:49:54.70,中文,,0,0,0,,刚好能刺穿颈动脉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Deep enough to puncture one wall of the carotid artery
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.70,0:49:56.60,中文,,0,0,0,,而又没有弄破颈动脉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}without rupturing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.60,0:49:59.97,中文,,0,0,0,,干净利落 下刀干脆 没有淤青或是伤痕\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Razor sharp, clean cut, no bruising, no trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.97,0:50:01.80,中文,,0,0,0,,没有任何工具能够做到这样的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's no instrument that can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.80,0:50:04.77,中文,,0,0,0,,总之我是不知道什么东西能做到这个程度 如此精准\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Not that I'm aware of, anyway, not with this precision.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.77,0:50:05.87,中文,,0,0,0,,还有其他发现吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.87,0:50:07.31,中文,,0,0,0,,这就更有趣了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Gets way more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.31,0:50:10.71,中文,,0,0,0,,其他六具尸体都是这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A spot check of six other corpses revealed the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.71,0:50:13.88,中文,,0,0,0,,同样的地方 同样的伤痕\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The exact same wound, in the exact same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.88,0:50:15.38,中文,,0,0,0,,你是说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Are you telling me
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.38,0:50:17.92,中文,,0,0,0,,其他乘客也有这样的切口吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that the other passengers have the same incision?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.92,0:50:19.12,中文,,0,0,0,,也可以说是穿刺\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Or puncture.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.12,0:50:21.49,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 到目前为止都是这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yes, all the ones I've looked at so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.49,0:50:24.52,中文,,0,0,0,,还有个有趣的反常的地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There is one more intriguing abnormality.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.94,0:50:40.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知 这是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't... what the hell am I looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.04,0:50:42.11,中文,,0,0,0,,我们这边看起来是白色的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}On our screen that looks white.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.11,0:50:44.14,中文,,0,0,0,,本来就是乳白色的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Because it is white and opalescent.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.15,0:50:46.08,中文,,0,0,0,,血蛋白在分离\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Blood proteins are separating.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.08,0:50:48.85,中文,,0,0,0,,不 实际上 尸体里根本就没有积血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, in fact, there's a complete absence of hypostasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.85,0:50:50.62,中文,,0,0,0,,没有血液沉积\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No blood pooling anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.62,0:50:52.62,中文,,0,0,0,,连红血细胞都没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And an absolute absence of erythrocytes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.62,0:50:55.62,中文,,0,0,0,,如果等我解剖了肝脏以后能获得更多信息\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll know more once I cut into the liver and kidneys but...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.62,0:50:57.06,中文,,0,0,0,,我也不想这么对你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm sorry to do this to you
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.06,0:50:59.56,中文,,0,0,0,,但你得单独做这些分析\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but you're gonna have to do the preliminary alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.56,0:51:01.86,中文,,0,0,0,,这事儿一点也不能透露给媒体\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't want any of this leaking to the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.86,0:51:03.46,中文,,0,0,0,,好啊 哥们 但你得欠我个人情了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, buddy, but you'll owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.46,0:51:05.33,中文,,0,0,0,,欠你一辈子人情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}For the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.33,0:51:06.63,中文,,0,0,0,,见鬼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.24,0:51:10.74,中文,,0,0,0,,伊弗 打扰一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Eph! I'm sorry but I think
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.74,0:51:13.14,中文,,0,0,0,,不过你可能想和他谈一谈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you're gonna want to talk to this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.91,0:51:19.21,中文,,0,0,0,,古德温泽博士 我是亚伯拉罕 塞特拉基安\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dr. Goodweather, my name is Abraham Setrakian.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.21,0:51:20.58,中文,,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's very nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.58,0:51:22.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我现在没法儿和你谈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can't talk right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.12,0:51:24.79,中文,,0,0,0,,伊弗 他说他知道这件事的内幕\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Eph, he says he has some insight into the outbreak here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.79,0:51:26.45,中文,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.45,0:51:29.22,中文,,0,0,0,,肯特 你能来记一下吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mr. Kent, here, can take down your information...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.22,0:51:30.69,中文,,0,0,0,,时间宝贵啊 博士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Time is of the essence, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.69,0:51:31.89,中文,,0,0,0,,确实如此 金\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It certainly is. Jim...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.89,0:51:32.99,中文,,0,0,0,,伊弗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Eph...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.99,0:51:34.63,中文,,0,0,0,,你必须听我说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You have to listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.63,0:51:37.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我以前见过这种疾病\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have seen this disease before.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.10,0:51:38.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我应对这种情况\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have faced it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.77,0:51:40.23,中文,,0,0,0,,你 你必须控制疫情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You... you must contain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.23,0:51:41.74,中文,,0,0,0,,你以前见过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You've seen it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.74,0:51:44.17,中文,,0,0,0,,我像你保证我们已经采取了必要的措施\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I assure you we're taking every available precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.17,0:51:45.51,中文,,0,0,0,,你没有 你也没法儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're not. You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.51,0:51:47.97,中文,,0,0,0,,而这样正中了他的下怀\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And he is counting on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.38,0:51:50.41,中文,,0,0,0,,他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"He?"
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.41,0:51:53.58,中文,,0,0,0,,我要是在这儿一次性说完来龙去脉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It is too much to say all at once here
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.58,0:51:56.52,中文,,0,0,0,,你肯定会觉得我疯了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}without sounding crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.05,0:51:58.95,中文,,0,0,0,,对 你没疯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.95,0:52:00.72,中文,,0,0,0,,呃 金 我们要去货仓看看\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Uh, Jim, we're going to the cargo hold
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.72,0:52:02.82,中文,,0,0,0,,帮我照看一下这位先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}please take care of this gentleman for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.82,0:52:03.82,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.83,0:52:05.23,中文,,0,0,0,,没关系的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.23,0:52:06.56,中文,,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.70,0:52:08.76,中文,,0,0,0,,那些尸体\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.76,0:52:11.13,中文,,0,0,0,,他们没有正常地腐烂掉 是吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They're not decomposing normally, yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.13,0:52:12.97,中文,,0,0,0,,组织都还是柔软的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The tissues are still pliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.97,0:52:15.04,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么知道 - 诺拉 诺拉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- How do you know that? - Nora, Nora...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.04,0:52:16.54,中文,,0,0,0,,听我说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Listen to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.54,0:52:19.34,中文,,0,0,0,,失敬了 但我必须得说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What I am about to say I do not say lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.34,0:52:21.41,中文,,0,0,0,,那班飞机上的所有乘客\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All the passengers on that plane
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.41,0:52:23.24,中文,,0,0,0,,不论死活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}dead and alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.08,0:52:27.65,中文,,0,0,0,,都必须摧毁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}they must be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.22,0:52:30.48,中文,,0,0,0,,摧毁 好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Destroyed? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.49,0:52:31.55,中文,,0,0,0,,把他带走 弟兄们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Here you go, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.55,0:52:32.82,中文,,0,0,0,,感觉好多了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.82,0:52:34.59,中文,,0,0,0,,必须把头砍掉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The heads must be severed!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.59,0:52:37.36,中文,,0,0,0,,把尸体烧掉 一定要摧毁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The bodies burned, destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.76,0:52:42.80,中文,,0,0,0,,博士 你找到棺材了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Doctor, did you find the coffin?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.80,0:52:45.70,中文,,0,0,0,,如果棺材还在你手里 那你就还能控制住他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If you have the coffin then you still have him!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.70,0:52:47.30,中文,,0,0,0,,亡羊补牢还来得及\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It is not too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.30,0:52:48.87,中文,,0,0,0,,摧毁棺材\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Destroy the coffin!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.87,0:52:51.51,中文,,0,0,0,,不要让它过河\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do not allow it across the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.19,0:53:03.78,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\bord0\fs50\pos(406,530)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}\h\h首席{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}法医{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)}办公室\N{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}曼哈顿{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)} 东{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)}30{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}街
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.88,0:53:04.59,中文,,0,0,0,,应古德温泽博士要求\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}As advised by Doctor Goodweather
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.59,0:53:07.65,中文,,0,0,0,,我将会在紫外灯下进行尸检\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I will examine the body under UV light.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.93,0:53:37.33,中文,,0,0,0,,那个老头是怎么知道棺材的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How did that old man know about the coffin?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.33,0:53:39.03,中文,,0,0,0,,你说那个箱子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You mean the cabinet?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.03,0:53:40.83,中文,,0,0,0,,他叫它棺材\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He called it a coffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.83,0:53:42.43,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道那个老头叫的是棺材\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know what he called it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.43,0:53:45.77,中文,,0,0,0,,他还叫我们毁了那206个尸体呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He also told us to destroy 206 bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.77,0:53:47.50,中文,,0,0,0,,他还有一把剑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And he had a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.11,0:53:51.27,中文,,0,0,0,,诺拉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nora.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.28,0:53:57.38,中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.58,0:54:00.02,中文,,0,0,0,,这特么是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.46,0:54:08.19,中文,,0,0,0,,像是一条铁线虫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Looks like a horsehair worm
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.19,0:54:10.79,中文,,0,0,0,,或者是犬恶丝虫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}or a Dirofilaria immitis.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.43,0:54:14.30,中文,,0,0,0,,构造很简单 只是胶原蛋白组织\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Body is simple. It's just collagen.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.30,0:54:17.30,中文,,0,0,0,,消化系统功能已经退化至丧失功能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Degenerate non-functional digestive system.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.64,0:54:21.84,中文,,0,0,0,,看这个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.84,0:54:23.41,中文,,0,0,0,,真美啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.41,0:54:26.61,中文,,0,0,0,,它在找寄主 极为迫切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's looking for a host, it's desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.92,0:54:41.82,中文,,0,0,0,,所以这不是通过空气传播的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So it's not airborne.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.03,0:54:44.66,中文,,0,0,0,,这就是载体\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's the carrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.07,0:54:52.97,中文,,0,0,0,,伊弗 看这些\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Eph, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.78,0:55:05.98,中文,,0,0,0,,泥土\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.91,0:55:24.50,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.50,0:55:26.34,中文,,0,0,0,,那个大箱子在哪儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where's that cabinet?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.34,0:55:27.44,中文,,0,0,0,,什么箱子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What cabinet?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.88,0:55:37.25,中文,,0,0,0,,这里 就这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There, right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.25,0:55:38.65,中文,,0,0,0,,倒带\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Rewind.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.65,0:55:40.65,中文,,0,0,0,,你能放慢一点吗 一帧一帧地放\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can you go slower, frame by frame?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.65,0:55:42.72,中文,,0,0,0,,这中间一定有断电或者被剪切了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There must be a gap or a cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.72,0:55:44.22,中文,,0,0,0,,不 没有剪切过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, there's not cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.22,0:55:46.16,中文,,0,0,0,,看时间轴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Watch the time code.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.16,0:55:50.69,中文,,0,0,0,,2秒 往前\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Two seconds. Go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.76,0:55:53.96,中文,,0,0,0,,从那儿开始\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Start there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.96,0:55:55.36,中文,,0,0,0,,等下 等下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.47,0:55:57.50,中文,,0,0,0,,就这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.60,0:56:02.30,中文,,0,0,0,,这一坨是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What's that distortion?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.31,0:56:04.34,中文,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.34,0:56:08.08,中文,,0,0,0,,它抓住了箱子然后提了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It grabs the box and lifts it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.08,0:56:10.45,中文,,0,0,0,,起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}up...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.65,0:56:12.65,中文,,0,0,0,,那个箱子有500磅重\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That box was 500 pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.65,0:56:14.45,中文,,0,0,0,,没东西能把它提起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nothing could lift it up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.45,0:56:17.92,中文,,0,0,0,,那个老头说的 如果棺材还在你手里 那你就还能控制住他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The old man said, "If you have the coffin, you still have him."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.32,0:56:20.32,中文,,0,0,0,,他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.93,0:56:27.23,中文,,0,0,0,,这个监控显示就在7分钟前\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This footage is only seven minutes old.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.23,0:56:30.57,中文,,0,0,0,,那箱子还在机场里面\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The box is still in the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.70,0:56:44.33,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\bord0\fs50\pos(690,534)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}肯{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}尼{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)}迪{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}机场{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)} 公用{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)}车{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}库
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.43,0:57:04.77,中文,,0,0,0,,啊哈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Uh huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.48,0:57:18.55,中文,,0,0,0,,这特么是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.72,0:57:21.32,中文,,0,0,0,,这群疯子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Crazy ass white boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.96,0:57:34.73,中文,,0,0,0,,快 快 快接电话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on, come on, pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.73,0:57:36.17,中文,,0,0,0,,金 你在哪儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Jim, where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.17,0:57:38.43,中文,,0,0,0,,在主车库门设卡检查\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}At the main garage door funnelling traffic out.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.44,0:57:40.04,中文,,0,0,0,,停下  停下  禁止所有人出入\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stop it, stop it! Stop everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.04,0:57:41.40,中文,,0,0,0,,紧急情况\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.40,0:57:43.91,中文,,0,0,0,,你得封锁机场周边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You need to seal off the perimeter of the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.91,0:57:45.31,中文,,0,0,0,,那个盒子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That box...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.31,0:57:47.34,中文,,0,0,0,,记得有许多花纹的盒子吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Remember the box with the markings on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.34,0:57:49.14,中文,,0,0,0,,记得  记得  柏林那边遗漏的货物\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, yeah, the Berlin cargo omit.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.15,0:57:50.21,中文,,0,0,0,,就是那个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.21,0:57:51.58,中文,,0,0,0,,现在仔细听我说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now listen carefully, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.58,0:57:54.85,中文,,0,0,0,,我们得阻止所有能容得下它的车辆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We need to stop all vehicles big enough to hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.85,0:57:57.45,中文,,0,0,0,,货车  卡车  都不准通过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No vans, no trucks, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.45,0:57:59.96,中文,,0,0,0,,大型车辆都不行  没有例外\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No big vehicles. No exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.96,0:58:03.06,中文,,0,0,0,,安全区域任何大型车辆都不得进出  收到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, no big vehicles in or out of the security zone. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.06,0:58:04.79,中文,,0,0,0,,好了  所有人听好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Right, everybody listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.79,0:58:06.70,中文,,0,0,0,,没有我的批准\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I want none of these trucks
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.70,0:58:09.93,中文,,0,0,0,,任何货车及大型车辆都不得放行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}big-sized vehicles released without my authorization.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.40,0:58:14.54,中文,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}C'mon...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.26,0:58:35.09,中文,,0,0,0,,停在那里  先生  我马上过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Pull up there, sir, I'll be right with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.09,0:58:37.26,中文,,0,0,0,,操  操  操\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Shit! Shit, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.10,0:58:48.50,中文,,0,0,0,,身份证和许可证\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}ID and permit.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.51,0:58:50.27,中文,,0,0,0,,好的  伙计\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, yeah, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.27,0:58:52.64,中文,,0,0,0,,真疯狂  发生了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Crazy what's happening, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.12,0:59:04.05,中文,,0,0,0,,你给我这个是什么意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What do you want me to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.63,0:59:12.90,中文,,0,0,0,,下车  打开货箱  先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Step out of the vehicle, open the cargo area, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.06,0:59:15.43,中文,,0,0,0,,下车\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Step out of the vehicle...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.43,0:59:17.41,中文,,0,0,0,,-别拿灯照我的脸  -下车\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Get the light out of my face! - Step out of the vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.41,0:59:18.67,中文,,0,0,0,,能让我先解了安全带吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can I get my seatbelt?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.25,0:59:31.05,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey. What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.74,0:59:35.14,中文,,0,0,0,,我要看身份证  他给了我这个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I asked for ID, he gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.22,0:59:43.95,中文,,0,0,0,,这是我们的车\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, well, this is one of our vehicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.95,0:59:45.37,中文,,0,0,0,,-你可以让他过去  -长官\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- You can let him through. - Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.37,0:59:46.66,中文,,0,0,0,,我说了  让他过去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I said, let him through.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.68,0:59:54.45,中文,,0,0,0,,你告诉那些贱货我不干了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You tell those sons of bitches I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.45,0:59:56.72,中文,,0,0,0,,这是我最后一次帮他们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I came through for them but now I am done.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.72,0:59:58.22,中文,,0,0,0,,听到没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You got it?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.10,1:00:05.23,中文,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, go.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.30,1:00:16.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我现在打开其中一具尸体的胸腔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have now removed the chest plate of one of the subjects
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.14,1:00:19.98,中文,,0,0,0,,发现\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and found...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.98,1:00:25.48,中文,,0,0,0,,心脏  肝脏以及肾脏中\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}abnormal neoplasms in the heart, liver...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.22,1:00:29.89,中文,,0,0,0,,都有不寻常的肿瘤\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and kidneys.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.66,1:00:36.69,中文,,0,0,0,,从生长情况来看不像是癌变体\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The growths do not seem like oncological aberrations
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.69,1:00:43.57,中文,,0,0,0,,更像是具备完整功能的器官\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but almost like new, fully functional organs.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.73,1:01:53.17,中文,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.37,1:01:55.41,中文,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.64,1:01:57.61,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.52,1:02:11.66,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Agh!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.82,1:02:56.58,中文,,0,0,0,,对不起  伊弗  没有发现\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sorry, Eph. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.89,1:02:57.92,中文,,0,0,0,,你这有什么进展吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You got anything here?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.46,1:02:59.17,中文,,0,0,0,,正在想办法搞清楚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just trying to figure out
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.20,1:03:02.86,中文,,0,0,0,,一具重达五百磅高九英尺的棺材是怎么被带走的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}how a 500-pound, 9-foot tall coffin got up and walked away.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.56,1:03:06.66,中文,,0,0,0,,你管那叫棺材\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You called it a coffin.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.07,1:03:07.75,中文,,0,0,0,,下次运气就不会这么差了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We'll get a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.93,1:03:09.00,中文,,0,0,0,,每次都是这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We always do.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.00,1:03:11.00,中文,,0,0,0,,现在要做的就是找到切入点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We just gotta find some place to start.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.74,1:03:16.64,中文,,0,0,0,,这就是我们的切入点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is where we start.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.64,1:03:18.34,中文,,0,0,0,,这是什么鬼东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What the hell are those?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.35,1:03:19.98,中文,,0,0,0,,新玩意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Something new.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.66,1:03:35.86,中文,,0,0,0,,塞-特-拉-基-安\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}S-e-t-r-a-k-I-a-n?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.02,1:03:37.65,中文,,0,0,0,,塞特拉基安\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Setrakian?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.65,1:03:39.16,中文,,0,0,0,,这是哪国名字\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What is... what is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.17,1:03:40.40,中文,,0,0,0,,亚美尼亚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Armenian.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.40,1:03:41.90,中文,,0,0,0,,你是从那来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is that where you're from?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.90,1:03:43.37,中文,,0,0,0,,曾经是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}At one time...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.91,1:03:47.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我什么时候可以走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How soon may I leave?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.37,1:03:49.17,中文,,0,0,0,,到周一才能立案\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, nothing happens 'til Monday.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.18,1:03:50.64,中文,,0,0,0,,到时候就知道了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The charges are filed then.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.64,1:03:52.21,中文,,0,0,0,,现在已经快天亮了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's almost dawn now.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.64,1:03:58.10,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\bord0\fs50\pos(446,522)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}皇后区{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)} 南{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)}牙买加{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)} 纽约{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)}警署{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)}113{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}分局
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.45,1:04:03.02,中文,,0,0,0,,你是图书管理员吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Are you the librarian?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.82,1:04:06.06,中文,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.06,1:04:09.29,中文,,0,0,0,,你胳膊上的印记够古老的  老头\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's some ancient ink you got there, old man.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.30,1:04:11.16,中文,,0,0,0,,写的什么  数字吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What is it, numbers?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.16,1:04:12.70,中文,,0,0,0,,是的  数字\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, numbers.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.14,1:04:16.20,中文,,0,0,0,,有什么意义吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mean anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.87,1:04:20.41,中文,,0,0,0,,只对我有意义\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Only to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.65,1:04:32.85,中文,,0,0,0,,一切都按计划进行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Everything went as planned.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.32,1:04:38.09,中文,,0,0,0,,爱会指引他们回家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Love is going to guide them all back
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.09,1:04:41.43,中文,,0,0,0,,回到心爱的人身边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to their homes, to their loved ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.86,1:04:47.17,中文,,0,0,0,,有件怪事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Curious detail...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.17,1:04:52.34,中文,,0,0,0,,一名携带佩剑的老人在机场被逮捕\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}an old man with a sword was arrested at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.14,1:04:56.47,中文,,0,0,0,,那个犹太人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The Jew.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.77,1:04:57.77,中文,,0,0,0,,他居然还活着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He's still at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.21,1:05:01.51,中文,,0,0,0,,经过了这么多年\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}After all these years.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.51,1:05:03.11,中文,,0,0,0,,就凭这点你也应该对他表示尊重\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You must admire him for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.12,1:05:05.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我来搞定他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.12,1:05:08.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我俯瞰这片岛屿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I look out upon this island
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.95,1:05:12.32,中文,,0,0,0,,慢慢品味这即将到来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and I savour what is to come...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.79,1:05:15.16,中文,,0,0,0,,纯净\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}purity.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.86,1:05:16.71,中文,,0,0,0,,费茨威廉先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mr. Fitzwilliam...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.68,1:05:21.10,中文,,0,0,0,,一个多愁善感的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}a sentimental man
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.10,1:05:23.13,中文,,0,0,0,,会在这一切降临之前\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}would venture out into the city tonight
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.14,1:05:26.00,中文,,0,0,0,,深入这座城市\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to walk these streets one last time...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.94,1:05:29.94,中文,,0,0,0,,将街头巷尾再走一遍\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}before the fall.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.48,1:05:33.01,中文,,0,0,0,,您还有别的吩咐吗  先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you require anything else, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.01,1:05:34.61,中文,,0,0,0,,没有了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.61,1:05:36.48,中文,,0,0,0,,生平第一次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}For the first time in my life
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.48,1:05:39.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我所需要的都已经拥有了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have everything I need.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.02,1:06:11.62,中文,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.69,1:06:12.65,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨 妈咪
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.28,1:06:14.20,中文,,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.70,1:06:15.40,中文,,0,0,0,,还能有谁
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.03,1:06:17.41,中文,,0,0,0,,你在抽烟吗
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.82,1:06:19.08,中文,,0,0,0,,什么  不  妈妈  我没抽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Huh? No, mommy, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.08,1:06:20.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我没抽烟  你开玩笑吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm not smoking. You kidding me or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.16,1:06:20.93,中文,,0,0,0,,我在工作\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm working.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.48,1:06:23.24,中文,,0,0,0,,就是打电话问问你在干什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just called to check in to see what you're up to.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.26,1:06:24.15,中文,,0,0,0,,克里斯宾在家吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is Crispin home?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.22,1:06:24.86,中文,,0,0,0,,他在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He is.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.37,1:06:28.83,中文,,0,0,0,,至少我能盯着他
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.85,1:06:31.58,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈  就剩一罐啤酒了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mama, one beer left.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.58,1:06:32.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你为什么要这样对我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why do you do this to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.79,1:06:34.45,中文,,0,0,0,,需要我说多少次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How many times do I gotta tell you?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.45,1:06:35.82,中文,,0,0,0,,我在给他做早饭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm making his breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.82,1:06:37.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我快到大桥了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm getting on the bridge now.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.52,1:06:38.47,中文,,0,0,0,,一小时之内到家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll be home in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.80,1:06:39.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.35,1:06:42.47,中文,,0,0,0,,我也爱你 儿子 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.38,1:06:49.11,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道你是什么  不过你给我带来了好运\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know what you are but you're bringing me good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.06,1:07:06.17,中文,,0,0,0,,爱是一种无法解释的力量\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Love, you see, is the one force that cannot be explained
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.34,1:07:10.91,中文,,0,0,0,,无法用化学的方式来理解\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}cannot be broken down into a chemical process.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.91,1:07:14.68,中文,,0,0,0,,它是指引我们回家的明灯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It is the beacon that guides us back home
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.68,1:07:16.65,中文,,0,0,0,,就算没有人在那里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}when no one is there
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.65,1:07:21.42,中文,,0,0,0,,那道光也会照亮前方迷途的路\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and the light that illuminates our loss.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.42,1:07:25.16,中文,,0,0,0,,爱的缺失会剥夺我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Its absence robs us of all pleasure
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.16,1:07:28.30,中文,,0,0,0,,感知快乐的能力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of our capacity for joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.30,1:07:33.77,中文,,0,0,0,,会让黑夜更加黑暗  白天黯淡无光\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It makes our nights darker and our days gloomier.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.68,1:07:43.31,中文,,0,0,0,,但当我们找到爱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But when we find love
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.31,1:07:48.02,中文,,0,0,0,,不管多畸形  多悲伤  多恶劣\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}no matter how wrong, how sad or how terrible
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.02,1:07:49.68,中文,,0,0,0,,我们紧紧抓住不放\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}we cling to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.00,1:07:52.46,中文,,0,0,0,,爱给我们力量\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It gives us our strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.68,1:07:55.24,中文,,0,0,0,,爱使我们屹立不倒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It holds us upright.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.55,1:08:00.73,中文,,0,0,0,,我们以爱为生  爱以我们为生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It feeds on us and we feed on it.
